## CORS — apply to every Netlify function response (including platform-level errors)
## This file is copied into dist/ by Vite and processed by Netlify CDN on deploy.

/api/*
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
  Access-Control-Allow-Headers: Content-Type, Authorization
  Access-Control-Allow-Methods: GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, OPTIONS
  Access-Control-Max-Age: 86400

/.netlify/functions/*
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
  Access-Control-Allow-Headers: Content-Type, Authorization
  Access-Control-Allow-Methods: GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, OPTIONS
  Access-Control-Max-Age: 86400
